    <div class="about__content">
      <div class="about__text">
        <h2 class="about__title">About Data Reflow</h2>
        <p class="about__description">
          Founded in 2020, Data Reflow was born from the frustration of seeing SMEs struggle with disconnected data systems.
          Our mission is to democratize enterprise-grade analytics, making powerful data insights accessible to businesses of all sizes.
        </p>
        <p class="about__description">
          Today, we serve over 2,500 businesses across retail, manufacturing, healthcare, and professional services,
          helping them achieve an average ROI of 340% within the first year.
        </p>
        <div class="about__stats">
          <div class="about__stat"
               data-controller="counter"
               data-counter-end-value="2500"
               data-counter-suffix-value="+"
               data-counter-separator-value=","
               data-counter-duration-value="3000">
            <div class="about__stat-number" data-counter-target="number">0+</div>
            <div class="about__stat-label">Happy Customers</div>
          </div>
          <div class="about__stat"
               data-controller="counter"
               data-counter-end-value="340"
               data-counter-suffix-value="%"
               data-counter-duration-value="2600">
